<p class="ql-align-center">最近，一段90后小伙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在工地木板上写书法的视频</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">受到广泛关注</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他的笔法行云流水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">颇有大家风范</p>
