<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>创业失败 工地谋生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>小伙自制“神笔”练字</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这位小伙名叫余尚景</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是云南昭通的一名钢筋工</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他说自己从小喜爱书法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大学期间曾多次获奖</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200922/2be969a7e44041728e8e1f5eccc62067.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为创业失败</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">余尚景欠下外债</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无奈到工地做钢筋工赚钱谋生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">即便如此</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他仍不想放弃书法爱好</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
